  // (B) in-office / hybrid / relocation CHECKBOX-question -> affirmative "Yes".
  const IO = /work from our|work out of our|in.?office|in person|able to work (from|hybrid)|onsite|on-site|relocat|willing.*office|local office|days (a|per) week|monday|tuesday|thursday|hybrid/;
